<section id="inicio" class="relative min-h-[calc(100vh-80px)] flex items-center overflow-hidden scroll-mt-20">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <img class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuB97v5_AB19Oz5QAS1p5C-rCkJx917ivCr0n1Ycgoh_SAqJp7PTXJ9EWz15G4CIAoptxF71f2Bp5dsPQgG33ykF2EePV0M3-0YycBL-ilZr9XI4riaBGOZjV9e0_vkeTfhiFJJgHu71aom06ovS03og6_kji_5Qx3_V1y9IXkfmYYy2YnqP_QJQidDAd9stQTzxCplpWD6hWW_YRT0lOf4pdQcVU7E2I4mPa83l9JFECU6NaCTMupTl7hFZVfY4CQoOha6yhkPJK58" alt="A cinematic, high-contrast shot of massive heavy machinery..."/>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 industrial-overlay"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 w-full px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop max-w-container-max mx-auto py-24">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
            <p class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface-variant uppercase mb-5">Escuela de Maquinaria Pesada en Chiclayo</p>
            <h1 class="font-headline-xl text-5xl md:text-headline-xl text-primary mb-6 uppercase">Aprende 6 máquinas al costo de una</h1>
            <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface mb-10 max-w-xl">
                Fórmate en operación y mantenimiento de maquinaria pesada con práctica en equipos reales, teoría aplicada y certificación por cada máquina aprendida.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
                <a class="bg-primary text-on-primary font-headline-md text-headline-md px-10 py-5 font-bold uppercase border-b-4 border-black active:translate-y-1 active:border-b-0 transition-all hover:bg-primary-container hover:text-on-primary-container text-center" href="#inscripcion">
                    Solicitar información
                </a>
                <a class="border-2 border-outline text-on-surface font-headline-md text-headline-md px-10 py-5 font-bold uppercase hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors text-center" href="#maquinas">
                    Ver máquinas
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 max-w-2xl">
                <div class="border border-outline-variant bg-surface-dim/70 p-4">
                    <strong class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary block">6 equipos</strong>
                    <span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Un programa integral</span>
                </div>
                <div class="border border-outline-variant bg-surface-dim/70 p-4">
                    <strong class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary block">Chiclayo</strong>
                    <span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Lambayeque, Perú</span>
                </div>
                <div class="border border-outline-variant bg-surface-dim/70 p-4">
                    <strong class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary block">Certificación</strong>
                    <span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Por máquina aprendida</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
